<dl><dt>Company Address:</dt><dd>PMB AN 364, Accra-North</dd></dl>
<dl><dt>Company Tel:</dt><dd>030 223 2116</dd></dl>
<dl><dt>Supplier #:</dt><dd>-</dd></dl>

